        {
            "id": "https://zenixp.com/blog/2f9f6fb3-87a2-8180-80b2-dabd192d9eca/",
            "url": "https://zenixp.com/blog/2f9f6fb3-87a2-8180-80b2-dabd192d9eca/",
            "title": "db-query skill 介绍",
            "date_published": "2026-01-30T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>db-query 是一个强大的 Clawdbot 技能，用于查询项目数据库并自动管理 SSH 隧道连接。</p>\n<h3 id=\"主要功能\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#主要功能\">#</a> 主要功能</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>自动管理 SSH 隧道生命周期</li>\n<li>支持多个数据库配置</li>\n<li>查询前自动建立隧道，查询后自动关闭</li>\n</ul>\n<p>📖 <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY2xhd2h1Yi5haS96ZW5peHAvZGItcXVlcnk=\">ClawHub 页面</span></p>\n<p>💻 <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3plbml4cC9kYi1xdWVyeS5za2lsbA==\">GitHub 仓库</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"使用方法\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#使用方法\">#</a> 使用方法</h3>\n<p>db-query 技能通过配置文件管理多个数据库连接，特别适合需要通过 SSH 隧道访问的数据库环境。</p>\n<h3 id=\"配置文件设置\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#配置文件设置\">#</a> 配置文件设置</h3>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># ~/.config/db-query/config.json</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">&quot;databases&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;production&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;description&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;生产环境数据库&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;host&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;localhost&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;port&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"number\">3306</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;database&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;myapp&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;username&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;db_user&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;ssh_tunnel&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attr\">&quot;host&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;prod-server.example.com&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attr\">&quot;user&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;deploy&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"attr\">&quot;port&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"number\">22</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">&quot;staging&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"punctuation\">&#123;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;description&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;测试环境数据库&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;host&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;localhost&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;port&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"number\">5432</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;database&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;myapp_staging&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">,</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">&quot;username&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;postgres&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"punctuation\">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"基本使用\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#基本使用\">#</a> 基本使用</h3>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 查询生产环境用户数据</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">db-query production <span class=\"string\">&quot;SELECT * FROM users WHERE active = 1 LIMIT 10&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 查询测试环境订单统计</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">db-query staging <span class=\"string\">&quot;SELECT status, COUNT(*) FROM orders GROUP BY status&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 不使用 SSH 隧道的本地查询</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">db-query <span class=\"built_in\">local</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;SELECT NOW()&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"高级功能\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#高级功能\">#</a> 高级功能</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>🔗 自动 SSH 隧道管理：查询前建立连接，完成后自动清理</li>\n<li>📊 结果格式化：支持 JSON、表格等多种输出格式</li>\n<li>🔐 安全连接：支持 SSH 密钥认证和密码认证</li>\n<li>⚡ 批量查询：一次执行多个 SQL 语句</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"适用场景\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#适用场景\">#</a> 适用场景</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>开发环境需要访问生产数据库进行数据调试</li>\n<li>CI/CD 流程中的数据库检查和数据迁移</li>\n<li>运维脚本中的数据库监控和统计</li>\n<li>多环境数据库的统一管理</li>\n</ul>\n",
            "tags": [
                "学习笔记",
                "clawdbot",
                "database",
                "ssh",
                "skill"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://zenixp.com/blog/29bf6fb3-87a2-80dd-b65f-fc92e19c09d9/",
            "url": "https://zenixp.com/blog/29bf6fb3-87a2-80dd-b65f-fc92e19c09d9/",
            "title": "Shoka主题的Hexo与Notion集成",
            "date_published": "2025-09-09T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>笔者是 notion 的重度使用用户，所以一直想把 notion 的页面直接转成 hexo 的页面，正好拿本站来实行我的想法，</p>\n<p>顺便简单介绍一下本站运转方式。</p>\n<p><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3plbml4cC9oZXhvLXNob2thLW5vdGlvbi5naXQ=\">源代码仓库</span></p>\n<h2 id=\"项目结构\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#项目结构\">#</a> <strong>项目结构</strong></h2>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><figcaption><span>text</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">├── source/                 # 源内容</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   ├── _posts/            # 生成的博客文章 (来自 Notion)</span><br><span class=\"line\">│   └── assets/            # 下载的资源 (图片)</span><br><span class=\"line\">├── themes/shoka/          # Shoka 主题文件</span><br><span class=\"line\">├── public/                # 生成的静态站点</span><br><span class=\"line\">├── _config.yml            # 主 Hexo 配置</span><br><span class=\"line\">├── _config.shoka.yml      # 主题配置</span><br><span class=\"line\">└── notion_sync.js         # Notion 同步脚本</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/29bf6fb3-87a2-80dd-b65f-fc92e19c09d9/1762423439334_image.png\" alt=\"image.png\" /></p>\n<h3 id=\"安装\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#安装\">#</a> <strong>安装</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>克隆仓库:</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git <span class=\"built_in\">clone</span> https://github.com/zenixp/hexo-shoka-notion.git</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> hexo-shoka-notion</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装依赖:</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yarn install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"配置\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#配置\">#</a> <strong>配置</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>设置 Notion integration:\n<ul>\n<li>创建一个 Notion integration 并获取您的令牌（具体如何获取下面会说）</li>\n<li>在  <code>.env</code>  文件中添加  <code>NOTION_TOKEN</code>  和  <code>NOTION_DATA_SOURCE</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>设置 waline:\n<ul>\n<li>waline 部署请参考 <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93YWxpbmUuanMub3JnL2d1aWRlL2dldC1zdGFydGVkLw==\">https://waline.js.org/guide/get-started/</span></li>\n<li>将地址配置到_config.yml 中</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">waline:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">url:</span> <span class=\"string\">http://your-waline-url</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>其他配置请参考原 <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9zaG9rYS5sb3N0eXUubWUvY29tcHV0ZXItc2NpZW5jZS9ub3RlL3RoZW1lLXNob2thLWRvYy8=\">Shoka 文档</span></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"开发命令\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#开发命令\">#</a> <strong>开发命令</strong></h3>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 启动本地开发服务器</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yarn run server</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 从 Notion 同步内容</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yarn run <span class=\"built_in\">sync</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 生成静态文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yarn run build</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 清除缓存文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yarn run clean</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 索引文章到 Algolia 搜索</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yarn run algolia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"notion-集成\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#notion-集成\">#</a> <strong>Notion 集成</strong></h2>\n<p>使用  <code>notion_sync.js</code>  脚本从 Notion 数据库中拉取内容。脚本会：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>从您的 Notion 数据库中获取已发布的文章</li>\n<li>将 Notion 页面转换为 Markdown 格式</li>\n<li>下载和管理图片和资源</li>\n<li>生成带有标签、分类和元数据的正确前言</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"如何获取notion的token\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#如何获取notion的token\">#</a> 如何获取 notion 的 token</h3>\n<p>打开 notion，我这里用的是 desktop 版</p>\n<p>打开 Settings &gt; Connections &gt; Develop or manage integrations</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/29bf6fb3-87a2-80dd-b65f-fc92e19c09d9/1762423442081_image.png\" alt=\"image.png\" /></p>\n<p>根据页面提示创建一个新的 integration</p>\n<p>进入到刚刚创建的 integration，把 secret 复制下载保存好，并确保 read 权限是勾起来的</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/29bf6fb3-87a2-80dd-b65f-fc92e19c09d9/1762423443178_image.png\" alt=\"image.png\" /></p>\n<h3 id=\"如何创建notion数据库\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#如何创建notion数据库\">#</a> 如何创建 notion 数据库</h3>\n<p>回到 notion 创建一个新页面，页面类型选择 Database，然后创建一个 table 作为 data_source</p>\n<p><strong>必需的 table 属性</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>Title</code>  (标题) - 文章标题</li>\n<li><code>Published</code>  (复选框) - 是否发布文章</li>\n<li><code>Date</code>  (日期) - 发布日期</li>\n<li><code>Tags</code>  (多选) - 文章标签</li>\n<li><code>Category</code>  (下拉) - 文章分类</li>\n<li><code>Cover</code>  (文件) - 文章封面图片</li>\n</ul>\n<p>创建好后我们要在 notion integration 里配置页面的访问权限</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/29bf6fb3-87a2-80dd-b65f-fc92e19c09d9/1762423444286_image.png\" alt=\"image.png\" /></p>\n<h3 id=\"如何获取data_source-id\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#如何获取data_source-id\">#</a> 如何获取 data_source id</h3>\n<p>回到 notion 右键左边我们刚刚创建的数据库菜单选择 copy link，会得到类似下面这样的链接，中间这个就是 database 的 id</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/29bf6fb3-87a2-80dd-b65f-fc92e19c09d9/1762423445492_image.png\" alt=\"image.png\" /></p>\n<p>但我们需要的是 data_source 的 id，所以需要用 postman 请求获取</p>\n<p>上面获取的 secret 就是我们请求需要的 token，然后将 data_sources.id 复制保存下来</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/29bf6fb3-87a2-80dd-b65f-fc92e19c09d9/1762423446423_image.png\" alt=\"image.png\" /></p>\n<p>将 secret 和 data_source 的 id 写到.env 文件中即可</p>\n<h2 id=\"部署\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#部署\">#</a> <strong>部署</strong></h2>\n<p>要部署您的博客，可以使用任何静态托管服务：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>构建流程:</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 从 Notion 同步内容</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yarn run <span class=\"built_in\">sync</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 同步内容到 algolia （如果有配置algolia）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yarn run algolia</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 生成静态文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yarn run build</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>将  <code>public/</code>  目录部署到任何静态文件托管服务</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n",
            "tags": [
                "学习笔记",
                "hexo",
                "shoka",
                "notion",
                "waline"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://zenixp.com/blog/299f6fb3-87a2-80fd-bb41-ccebb300392d/",
            "url": "https://zenixp.com/blog/299f6fb3-87a2-80fd-bb41-ccebb300392d/",
            "title": "使用docker-compose安装gitlab和gitlab-runner",
            "date_published": "2025-09-08T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<p>本文记录使用 Docker Compose 部署 GitLab 与 GitLab Runner 的完整流程与常见踩坑，附可直接使用的示例配置与排错指引。</p>\n<hr />\n<h3 id=\"前置准备\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#前置准备\">#</a> 前置准备</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>已安装 Docker 与 Docker Compose（参考<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9kb2NzLmRvY2tlci5jb20vZW5naW5lL2luc3RhbGwv\">官方文档</span>）</li>\n<li>新建项目目录，例如 gitlab，并在目录内编写 docker-compose.yml</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"docker-composeyml-示例\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#docker-composeyml-示例\">#</a> docker-compose.yml 示例</h3>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">services:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">gitlab:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">image:</span> <span class=\"string\">gitlab/gitlab-ce:latest</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">restart:</span> <span class=\"string\">always</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">privileged:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">hostname:</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">localhost</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">container_name:</span> <span class=\"string\">gitlab</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">environment:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">GITLAB_OMNIBUS_CONFIG:</span> <span class=\"string\">|</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">        external_url &#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"></span><span class=\"string\">http://example:8888</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&#x27;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">        gitlab_rails[&#x27;</span><span class=\"string\">gitlab_shell_ssh_port&#x27;]</span> <span class=\"string\">=</span> <span class=\"number\">2222</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">ports:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;8888:8888&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;8443:443&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;2222:22&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">volumes:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">./config:/etc/gitlab</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">./logs:/var/log/gitlab</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">./data:/var/opt/gitlab</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">networks:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">gitlab</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">gitlab-runner:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">image:</span> <span class=\"string\">gitlab/gitlab-runner:alpine</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">container_name:</span> <span class=\"string\">gitlab-runner</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">restart:</span> <span class=\"string\">always</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">depends_on:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">gitlab</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">volumes:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">/var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">./gitlab-runner:/etc/gitlab-runner</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">networks:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">gitlab</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">networks:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">gitlab:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">name:</span> <span class=\"string\">gitlab-network</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>提示：示例中 HTTP 暴露为 8888，SSH 暴露为 2222，请确保与 external_url 及容器内部端口保持一致。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr />\n<h3 id=\"踩坑记录\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#踩坑记录\">#</a> 踩坑记录</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>踩坑 1：端口必须一致\n<ul>\n<li>映射端口、容器内部端口与 external_url 中端口需一致。</li>\n<li>避免使用 8080，会冲突。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>踩坑 2：Windows 挂载权限问题\n<ul>\n<li>宿主机为 Windows 时，推荐使用 “命名卷” 挂载，避免 Runner 上传 Artifacts 时出现 “目录无权限” 错误。参考：</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">services:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">gitlab:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># ...</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">volumes:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;gitlab-config:/etc/gitlab&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;gitlab-logs:/var/log/gitlab&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;gitlab-data:/var/opt/gitlab&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># ...</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">gitlab-runner:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># ...</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">volumes:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">/var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;gitlab-runner:/etc/gitlab-runner&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># ...</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">volumes:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">gitlab-runner:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">driver:</span> <span class=\"string\">local</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">gitlab-config:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">driver:</span> <span class=\"string\">local</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">gitlab-logs:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">driver:</span> <span class=\"string\">local</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">gitlab-data:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">driver:</span> <span class=\"string\">local</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>相关讨论见：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9mb3J1bS5naXRsYWIuY29tL3QvNTAwLWludGVybmFsLWVycm9yLXdoZW4tdHJ5aW5nLXRvLXVwbG9hZC1hcnRpZmFjdHMvNDM3MDkvOA==\">Runner 上传归档权限问题</span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr />\n<h3 id=\"启动服务\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#启动服务\">#</a> 启动服务</h3>\n<p>在项目目录下执行：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker-compose up -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>首次拉取与初始化较慢，请耐心等待。随后获取默认管理员密码：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker <span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> -it gitlab <span class=\"built_in\">cat</span> /etc/gitlab/initial_root_password</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<hr />\n<h3 id=\"注册-runner\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#注册-runner\">#</a> 注册 Runner</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>登陆 GitLab 后台，在 “管理员” 页面创建 Runner。</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/299f6fb3-87a2-80fd-bb41-ccebb300392d/1763050885957_img_1.png\" alt=\"img_1.png\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>复制创建完成后的 Token。</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/299f6fb3-87a2-80fd-bb41-ccebb300392d/1763050886769_img.png\" alt=\"img.png\" /></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>执行注册命令（将 url 与 token 替换为实际值）：</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker <span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> -it gitlab-runner \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  gitlab-runner register \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  --url </span><br><span class=\"line\">http://example:8888</span><br><span class=\"line\"> \\</span><br><span class=\"line\">  --token youtoken</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<hr />\n<h3 id=\"runner-常用配置\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#runner-常用配置\">#</a> Runner 常用配置</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>避免每次都重新拉取镜像（config.toml）：</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight toml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">[[runners]]</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"section\">[runners.docker]</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">pull_policy</span> = <span class=\"string\">&quot;if-not-present&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<ul>\n<li>直接在 Runner 内使用宿主机 Docker：</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight toml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"section\">[[runners]]</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"section\">[runners.docker]</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">volumes</span> = [<span class=\"string\">&quot;/var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock&quot;</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<hr />\n",
            "tags": [
                "学习笔记",
                "docker",
                "docker-compose",
                "gitlab"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://zenixp.com/blog/2a1f6fb3-87a2-80ed-81b3-fe18fe6ac865/",
            "url": "https://zenixp.com/blog/2a1f6fb3-87a2-80ed-81b3-fe18fe6ac865/",
            "title": "部署nexus作为docker镜像的私有仓库",
            "date_published": "2025-07-08T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h3 id=\"前言\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#前言\">#</a> 前言</h3>\n<p>在学习 k8s 时，打包应用镜像，需要搭建 docker 私有仓库，网路上主流都是用 harbor，但 harbor 部署时占用了太多资源，对于使用过 maven 私有库的人应该不陌生的 nexus 就可以拿来作为 docker 私有仓库来使用。</p>\n<h3 id=\"部署\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#部署\">#</a> 部署</h3>\n<p>这里使用 docker-compose 来部署</p>\n<p>创建 docker-compose.yml</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">services:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">nexus:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">container_name:</span> <span class=\"string\">nexus</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">image:</span> <span class=\"string\">sonatype/nexus3</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">volumes:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">./nexus-data:/nexus-data</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">ports:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"number\">8081</span><span class=\"string\">:8081</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">restart:</span> <span class=\"string\">on-failure</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">network_mode:</span> <span class=\"string\">bridge</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>执行下面命令启动容器</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker-compose up -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"配置\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#配置\">#</a> 配置</h3>\n<p>第一次登录默认账号是 admin，默认密码在./nexus-data/admin.password</p>\n<p>启动后默认已经有 maven 和 nuget 的私库配置，但是没有 docker 的，需要我们自己创建</p>\n<p>进入菜单 Settings &gt; Repository &gt; Repositories，点击 Create repository 创建仓库，类型选择 docker (hosted)</p>\n<p>Name 这里设置成 docker-hosted 或者自己写一个</p>\n<p>Allow anonymous docker pul 勾起来，其他默认配置即可</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/2a1f6fb3-87a2-80ed-81b3-fe18fe6ac865/1762394726616_image.png\" alt=\"image.png\" /></p>\n<h3 id=\"使用\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#使用\">#</a> 使用</h3>\n<p>创建好后使用下面命令就可以把镜像推送到私有仓库了</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker login &lt;你的域名或者ip地址&gt;:8081 -u admin -p &lt;admim密码&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">docker build -t &lt;你的域名或者ip地址&gt;:8081/docker-hosted/image:tag .</span><br><span class=\"line\">docker push &lt;你的域名或者ip地址&gt;:8081/docker-hosted/image:tag</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>docker 默认使用的是 https，服务只能通过 http 访问时需要在 daemon.json 里添加下面配置允许 http</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight json\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">&quot;insecure-registries&quot;</span><span class=\"punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"punctuation\">[</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"string\">&quot;&lt;你的域名或者ip地址&gt;:8081&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"punctuation\">]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "学习笔记",
                "nexus",
                "docker",
                "docker-compose"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://zenixp.com/blog/2a2f6fb3-87a2-8028-a6e1-eac908237d48/",
            "url": "https://zenixp.com/blog/2a2f6fb3-87a2-8028-a6e1-eac908237d48/",
            "title": "搭建softether 随时随地访问本地资源",
            "date_published": "2025-05-04T16:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"前言\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#前言\">#</a> 前言</h2>\n<p>在进行大型项目外包或协作时，经常需要通过 VPN 访问私有代码仓库或内网资源。本文演示如何使用 <a href=\"https://www.softether.org/\"><strong>SoftEther</strong></a> 快速搭建一个稳定、易用的开发访问环境。</p>\n<p><strong>SoftEther</strong> 由日本筑波大学开发，是一款开源的多协议 VPN 平台，支持多种连接方式。想进一步了解其功能与特性，可前往<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc29mdGV0aGVyLm9yZy8=\">官网</span>查看。</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"服务端\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#服务端\">#</a> 服务端</h2>\n<p>准备一台拥有公网 IP 的服务器用于运行 VPN 服务，对硬件要求不高。本文使用 Docker 部署。</p>\n<p>创建 docker-compose.yml：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">services:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">softethervpn:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">container_name:</span> <span class=\"string\">softethervpn</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">image:</span> <span class=\"string\">siomiz/softethervpn</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">cap_add:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">NET_ADMIN</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">ports:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;10443:443/tcp&quot;</span> <span class=\"comment\"># OpenVPN over HTTPS</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;500:500/udp&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;4500:4500/udp&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"bullet\">-</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;1701:1701/tcp&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attr\">environment:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">SPW:</span> <span class=\"string\">&lt;服务端管理密码&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">HPW:</span> <span class=\"string\">&lt;默认</span> <span class=\"string\">Hub（&quot;DEFAULT&quot;）的密码&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">      <span class=\"attr\">PSK:</span> <span class=\"string\">notasecret</span> <span class=\"comment\"># L2TP/IPSec 共享密钥</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>启动容器：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker-compose up -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>请在云服务控制台或防火墙中放通上述端口。</p>\n<p>接着<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc29mdGV0aGVyLWRvd25sb2FkLmNvbS9jbi5hc3B4P3Byb2R1Y3Q9c29mdGV0aGVy\">下载</span>服务端管理工具：</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/2a2f6fb3-87a2-8028-a6e1-eac908237d48/1763057114522_image.png\" alt=\"image.png\" /></p>\n<p>以下以 Windows 版为例进行说明。打开管理工具，使用 &lt;服务器 IP&gt;:10443 连接至服务端，密码为 docker-compose.yml 中的 SPW。</p>\n<p>进入后选择「管理虚拟 Hub」，用于管理用户与访问策略。先点击「虚拟 NAT 和虚拟 DHCP 服务器」，确保 SecureNAT 已启用，然后进入「SecureNAT 配置」。在此可设置 VPN 的虚拟网段，建议避开与本地网络重复的网段。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>建议：将「应用到客户端的选项」留空，可避免 “全流量走 VPN”，仅让虚拟网卡网段内的流量走 VPN。</li>\n<li>如需全量流量经服务端转发，可将默认网关设置为虚拟网卡地址。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/2a2f6fb3-87a2-8028-a6e1-eac908237d48/1763057115386_image.png\" alt=\"image.png\" /></p>\n<p>至此，服务端配置完成。</p>\n<hr />\n<h2 id=\"客户端\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#客户端\">#</a> 客户端</h2>\n<h3 id=\"linux\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#linux\">#</a> Linux</h3>\n<p>Linux 客户端配置相对繁琐，可使用笔者整理好的<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3plbml4cC9zb2Z0ZXRoZXItc2NyaXB0cy5naXQ=\">脚本</span>：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">git pull </span><br><span class=\"line\">https://github.com/zenixp/softether-scripts.git</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">cd softether-scripts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>然后从官网下载对应版本的 Linux 客户端：</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/2a2f6fb3-87a2-8028-a6e1-eac908237d48/1763057116461_2025-11-13_18.24.58.png\" alt=\"%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2025-11-13_18.24.58.png\" /></p>\n<p>将压缩包放到项目目录后执行安装脚本：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sh client_</span><br><span class=\"line\">install.sh</span><br><span class=\"line\"> softether-vpnclient-v4.43-9799-beta-2023.08.31-linux-x64-64bit.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>创建账户（username 和 password 为服务端「用户管理」中创建的账号密码）：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sh </span><br><span class=\"line\">create.sh</span><br><span class=\"line\"> --server &lt;服务器IP或域名:10443&gt; --username &lt;用户名&gt; --password &lt;密码&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>启动连接并为客户端虚拟网卡设置静态 IP。该 IP 需位于服务端 DHCP 配置的网段内；若子网掩码为 255.255.255.0，请在 IP 后加 /24：</p>\n<p><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sh </span><br><span class=\"line\">start.sh</span><br><span class=\"line\"> 192.168.86.100/24</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>可将启动脚本加入 crontab 或配置为 systemd service 实现开机自启。其他用法参考<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL3plbml4cC9zb2Z0ZXRoZXItc2NyaXB0cy9ibG9iL21haW4vUkVBRE1FX0NOLm1k\">文档</span>。</p>\n<h3 id=\"windows\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#windows\">#</a> Windows</h3>\n<p>从官网<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc29mdGV0aGVyLWRvd25sb2FkLmNvbS9jbi5hc3B4P3Byb2R1Y3Q9c29mdGV0aGVy\">下载</span>对应版本的客户端。</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"../assets/2a2f6fb3-87a2-8028-a6e1-eac908237d48/1763057117174_2025-11-13_23.14.07.png\" alt=\"%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2025-11-13_23.14.07.png\" /></p>\n<p>安装完成后，打开客户端，依次点击「连接」&gt;「新 VPN 连接设置」。首次新建会自动创建虚拟网卡。</p>\n<p>按服务端配置填写红框内信息，选择虚拟网卡后点击「确定」。</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/2a2f6fb3-87a2-8028-a6e1-eac908237d48/1763057117860_image.png\" alt=\"image.png\" /></p>\n<p>右键刚创建的连接，点击「连接」即可。右键选择「启动连接设置」可实现开机自启动。若需要静态 IP，可在系统网络设置中找到该虚拟网卡并配置。</p>\n<h3 id=\"macos-与-ios\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#macos-与-ios\">#</a> macOS 与 iOS</h3>\n<p>macOS 与 iOS 可使用系统内置 L2TP：</p>\n<p>设置 &gt; VPN &gt; 添加 VPN 设置，选择 L2TP。</p>\n<p><img data-src=\"/assets/2a2f6fb3-87a2-8028-a6e1-eac908237d48/1763057119055_image.png\" alt=\"image.png\" /></p>\n<p>配置与 Windows 基本一致，服务器地址无需填写端口。共享密钥填写 docker-compose.yml 中的 PSK（默认 notasecret）。如需静态 IP，可在「TCP/IP」中配置。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>iOS 提示：若服务端未配置默认网关，请关闭「发送所有流量」，否则可能无法上网。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p>完成以上配置后，便可通过 VPN 随时随地访问本地资源。</p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "学习笔记",
                "docker",
                "softether",
                "vpn"
            ]
        }
    ]
}